animeDescription: The story takes place in the era of the gods, year 300. Yuuna Yuuki lives an ordinary life as a second year middle school student, but she's also a member of the "Hero Club," where club activities involve dealing with a mysterious being called "Vertex."(Source: ANN)
animeRelated: ['Adaptation: Yuuki Yuuna wa Yuusha-bu Shozoku', 'Other: Yuuki Yuuna wa Yuusha de Aru', 'Sequel: Yuuki Yuuna wa Yuushabu Shozoku 2']
